    <refnamediv>
        <refname>gl_InstanceID</refname>
        <refpurpose>contains the index of the current primitive in an instanced draw command</refpurpose>
    </refnamediv>
    <refsynopsisdiv><title>Declaration</title>
        <para>
            <function>in int gl_InstanceID;</function>
        </para>
    </refsynopsisdiv>
    <refsect1 id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>gl_InstanceID</function> is a vertex language input variable that
            holds the integer index of the current primitive in an instanced draw
            command such as <function>glDrawArraysInstanced</function>. If the current
            primitive does not originate from an instanced draw command, the value
            of <function>gl_InstanceID</function> is zero.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
